a:17:{s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";s:11:"small_descr";s:88:"Himplasia is used to maintain a healthy prostate and an effective reproductive function.";s:14:"small_descr_de";s:100:"Himplasia wird verwendet, um eine gesunde Prostata und eine wirksame Geschlechtsfunktion zu halten. ";s:14:"small_descr_fr";s:86:"Himplasia est utilisée pour maintenir la santé de la prostate et de la procréation.";s:14:"small_descr_es";s:91:"Himplasia es utilizada para mantener una próstata sana y una función reproductiva eficaz.";s:14:"small_descr_it";s:86:"Himplasia si usa per mantenere una prostata sana e una funzione riproduttiva efficace.";s:10:"full_descr";s:1115:"<p><strong>INDICATIONS</strong></p><p>Himplasia is a herbal ayurvedic formulation that promotes optimum prostate health, urogenital function, bladder function and reproductive function. Himplasia is a non-hormonal herbal blend which helps maintain a healthy prostrate and an effective reproductive function.</p><p><strong>INSTRUCTIONS</strong></p><p>Take exactly as prescribed by your Health Provider.</p><p><strong>DOSAGE</strong></p><p>Please consult your Health Provider to prescribe the dosage that best suits your condition.</p><p>Usually 1 or 2 tablets twice daily with meals is recommended. Allow several weeks for benefits.</p><p><strong>STORAGE</strong></p><p>Store at the room temperature away from moisture, heat and sunlight. Keep out of reach of children and away from pets.</p><p><strong>SAFETY INFORMATION</strong></p><p>Himplasia should be used with caution in patients with hypertension. Please also inform your doctor if you are already on any diuretic medication.</p><p><strong>SIDE EFFECTS</strong></p><p>Himplasia is not known to have any side effects if taken as per the prescribed dosage.</p>";s:13:"full_descr_de";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_fr";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_es";s:0:"";s:13:"full_descr_it";s:0:"";s:9:"min_price";s:8:"22.14336";s:9:"pack_name";s:7:"bottles";s:4:"type";s:4:"caps";s:7:"analogs";N;s:18:"active_ingredients";N;s:8:"packings";a:1:{i:30;a:10:{i:5413;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5413";s:5:"count";s:1:"1";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"36.9056";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5414;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5414";s:5:"count";s:1:"2";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"28.70436";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5415;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5415";s:5:"count";s:1:"3";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"25.97061";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5416;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5416";s:5:"count";s:1:"4";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"24.60373";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5417;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5417";s:5:"count";s:1:"5";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"23.78361";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5418;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5418";s:5:"count";s:1:"6";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"23.23686";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5419;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5419";s:5:"count";s:1:"7";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"22.84632";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5420;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5420";s:5:"count";s:1:"8";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"22.55342";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5421;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5421";s:5:"count";s:1:"9";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"22.32561";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}i:5422;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"5422";s:5:"count";s:2:"10";s:6:"dosage";d:30;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:8:"22.14336";s:4:"name";s:9:"Himplasia";}}}}